My country has been in a downward trajectory in development. From any angle you want to look at it
On multiple occasions, the rights of citizens are undermined and even outrightly violated. Young people have been killed and maimed for protesting our previous government

The government is riddled w unbelievable degrees of corruption and are seen to have obvious intentions to keep the citizens poor and divided. They incite tribalist and religiously intolerant discourse and even activities in the country in other to keep the citizens subjugated while they loot the country dry
Elections were held on Saturday and for the first time, young people were enthusiastic to vote because a new candidate, who was different from the statutory politician were used to emerged.

Note that the “independent” body meant to conduct the elections had assured citizens that the new tech it adopted was going to ensure for maximum transparency in the elections and full trusts in the results

I have no idea why I believed it since all this government has done is low. But we did believe and came out en masse to vote. On Election Day, voters were disenfranchised by no fault of there’s. Some injured and other killed. Logistics didn’t get to their polling units on time and a bunch of hullabaloo

The major trust in the conductance of the election was based on the fact that the results of the elections were going to be electronically transmitted from polling units to the collation centres. If there were discrepancies on the collation centre at the federal level, the uploaded result takes precedence

Now, the “independent” body that’s meant to organize this election has refused to show the citizens what has been uploaded as citizens are themselves noticing discrepancies in results from their polling units different from the ones being called at the federal collation centres.

Letters have been written and protests are being protested. But said independent body is going on w the collations of the results anyway. 
The body meant to conduct the elections (if you haven’t already picked up) is not independent and is being paid up by the ruling party to retain power

The rigging is so evident and blatant it’s disgusting. The ruling party that’s currently winning keeps threatening other candidates to go to court. Our judiciary which has been paid for already. A rotten system from top to ground.
